{"tid":1537511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖教你點對抗狗鐵","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:43:59.000Z","uid":64601,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b848250b471d10a4caffea5414ba7c87156d2980","tid":1537511,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oatt6K8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foatt6K8.png&h=27ba3855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/financialinfo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Ffinancialinfo.html&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3KooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=68305846\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/financialinfo.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂：（排名以先後為主）<br />\n1. 抵制地鐵，搵可取代嘅交通<br />\n2. 抵制入面嘅廣告商<br />\n3. 抵制喺佢物業內經營嘅商戶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnote:除咗降低收入外，提升成本亦都係一個可行嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：唔好做犯法嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3919ac07ec592ea615d8010dd6569346df88a93","tid":1537511,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f0f874975ca5618cae25f107a3d044ced7a1b5","tid":1537511,"uid":60398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"